</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="o">//</span> <span class="ss">verify</span> <span class="ss">arithmetic</span> <span class="ss">result</span>
<span class="o">?-</span> <span class="m">114514</span> <span class="ss">is</span> <span class="m">1919</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="m">112595</span><span class="p">.</span>
<span class="ss">true</span>

<span class="o">//</span> <span class="ss">perform</span> <span class="ss">calculation</span>
<span class="o">?-</span> <span class="nv">X</span> <span class="ss">is</span> <span class="m">114514</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="m">1919810</span><span class="p">.</span>
<span class="nv">X</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="m">2034324</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>此外, 我们还可以在定义谓词时使用预置运算符:</p>

<div class="language-prolog highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
